{"tid":409899,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【「飛天意粉神教」註冊台灣宗教團體】","createTime":"2017-09-22T12:30:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T16:22:05.000Z","uid":89349,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc643094f0f2eb901b9f9d23a3a0adb4a6f01594","tid":409899,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:30:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/22/202851_18e64add3b00a70c459c9bdaddb4a5c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F22%2F202851_18e64add3b00a70c459c9bdaddb4a5c8.jpg&h=25c423fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣上月批准「飛天意粉神教」（又稱飛天意麵神教）成立宗教法人，將成為亞洲區首個獲政府認可的「飛天意粉神教」組織。 <br />\n<br />\n該團的宗旨為：「以人文主義來宣揚飛天麵神的愛與真理，平衡宗教影響力並保障世俗權利，尋求跨領域合作解決社會問題。」 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[url]全文︰<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/09-22-2017/41645\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F09-22-2017%2F41645&d=zO%2FjE4h7bd6oxmBH%2BWRXN5Uc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=b50617f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/09-22-2017/41645</a> [/url]"},{"pid":"5fbbde8cbf6a271cecd5548e2ff1df6d338f948c","tid":409899,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T15:56:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f2e2a2e04da8425e8cd7af641e81be23ebb080","tid":409899,"uid":127292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T23:51:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8be72303df206055983a8395d190ca254433c38","tid":409899,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T01:26:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台灣啲耶撚有冇屌佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一定有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa7b7822ee78d8ce8350cc7cbf2379fdec2d4c4a","tid":409899,"uid":32439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T01: